@Slow Hand @cian riordan I think it's an algamation of things, scene change is definitely part of it, for some personal and cultural reasons 

I've also just been seeking out more weird shit, music wise. I went to this commercial songwriting school a decade ago where a bunch of fancy A&Rs would come and feedback our writing and tell us what's what, what we should think is good etc, and I think I carried a lot of that with me until very recently, even in my listening habits.

I guess I just don't really give a shit anymore, and just follow what I enjoy. It rocks.

Unfortunately I missed a very important one. 

